column2: Nice day- algae bloom started about 4-6 days ago.  Lake level: Slightly above average 6"
Mild wind and waves.  Lake level: Slightly above average 6"
Windy- rain and very cold the last three days.
Windy- rain- cold- and white caps on the lake last four days.
Rain on and off past three days also below normal temperatures.
Lake is great for this time of year. Cool water.
Lake water is great- cool.  Lots of big high powered boats.  Small amount of bloom.
10 people have reported swimmers itch to me- 13' is the deepest reading this summer
Have had a lot of dark windy days in the past weeks.
Some bloom pollen on windward side of lake.
Beautiful clear day- 19 feet is the clearest the water has been in the last 2 years.
Public perception due to swimmer's itch.  Some very bad cases of swimmer's itch- including myself.
Public perception due to swimmer's itch.  Beautiful clear water- some itch.
Windy rainy days.  High water level - above normal for this time of year.  Lake level: very high
Lake level 6" above normal- beautiful clear water- partially cloudy day.
Partly cloudy- humid- 80 degrees- and a light breeze.
Partly cloudy and a slight breeze.
Warm- sunny day- upper 80's- light breeze.
Clear skies- northwest winds that are fairly strong.  Water level: up 2"
Clear skies- sunny- wind is calm.
Clear skies- winds almost nil- and calm water.
Partly cloudy- rained 2 days prior to sample.
Mostly cloudy.  Lake level: Very high 5" to 6" above normal
Partly cloudy. starting to see some algal blooms.
Clear sky- saw sea gulls- pair of loons.
Winds- calm- water is like glass- only one loon on lake.
Water is gray.  Mostly cloudy and cool.  Water level: up 2"
Loose weeds floating on water.  Partly cloudy and breezy.  Passed one loon on the way to test site.
Cloudy and 62 degrees.  I heard loons.
Sunny and clear with a temperature of 80 degrees.  Lots of algae on the east shore for about 5 days.  Saw 3 loons.
Partly sunny and 80 degrees.  Saw 12 ducks on east shore.
Sunny and clear with a temperature of 82 degrees.  Saw 11 ducks on the northeast shore.
Partly cloudy and 72 degrees.  Water temperature is 74 degrees.  Saw 2 loons.
Partly cloudy and 75 degrees.  Weeds are more numerous.  Saw one loon.
Partly cloudy and 75 degrees.  Saw one loon.
Clear windy (from the northwest) and 75 degrees.  Saw 3 loons.
Clear and 78 degrees with no wind.  Water temperature is 78 degrees.
Partly cloudy and 75 degrees with southwest winds.
Sunny and 74 degrees with westerly winds.  Saw 3 loons.
Cloudy and 62 degrees with westerly winds.
Air temp 82 F- clear sky. water 72 F.
Temp 80 F- sunny- slight breeze from the south.
Temp 64 F- cloudy- partly sunny- 1 loon- muskrats galore- active.
Temp 70 F- partly cloudy- muskrats on NE shore- bit small dog.
Mostly cloudy with haze- 2 loons- 2 ducks- 1 muskrat- temp 75 F.
Clear- sunny- temp 81 F- windy from west.
Partly cloudy- air temp 72 F- calm wind- 1 loon.
Partly cloudy- temp 80 F- calm wind- 3 loons.
Partly cloudy- temp 68 F- 1 loon- muskrats frequently seen on NE shore.
Clear sky- temp 78 F.  Water 72 F.
2 severe thunderstorms yesterday- 4:30 and 6:30 pm. Hail in the 4:30 storm. WSW wind 5-10 mph. Partly cloudy.
NW wind 10-15 mph. Lots of boat traffic. 80 deg F. Temps have been in the 80's and 90's all week. Sunny.
NW wind 7-12 mph. Mostly cloudy. 70 deg F.
NW wind 5-10 mph. Partly cloudy. 70 deg F. Algae bloom.
SW wind 10-15 mph. Sunny and 68 deg F.
NW wind 10-15 mph. Partly cloudy. 66 deg F.
WSW wind 5-10 mph. Sunny and 43 deg F.
Partly cloudy- 5-10 mph SSE wind- 1 pair of loons on lake
Mostly sunny. Light NNW wind. Very heavy boat and jet ski traffic.
Sunny    Air Temp. 70   Light variable direction winds
Partly cloudy. Light NW wind. Air temperature 68
Sunny. Hazy - very high humidity. Air temp. - 80
Sunny.   Wind: S 5-10mph  1 pr. loons and 50 ducks on
Mostly sunny. 5-10MPH NE wind. Many boats on lake May
Sunny. 0-5 mph SW wind. 2 boats on lake. One eagle was

column1: getting fish from lake in the early morning.

column2: Partly Sunny.  5-10 mph NW wind. 1 loon on lake.
Partly cloudy. NNE 5-10 mph wind. No boats on lake. 2

column1: loons on lake. Air temp. 71 degrees.

column2: Sunny and humid. 0-5 mph SE wind. Air temp. 77
Sunny. Calm. Hazy + Humid. No boats on lake. Air temp.
Sunny. Air temp. 69 degrees. SW wind 0-5 mph. No boats

column1: on lake. To loons on lake. Lake is down approx. 12" since the ice went out

column2: NNW wind 5-10 mph. Mostly sunny. 2 pair of loons on lake. No boats on lake.
WSW wind - 0-5 mph. Partly Cloudy. 3 fishing boats on lake. Air temp. - 66 degrees F.
SW wind 0-5 mph. Partly cloudy. 2 pleasure boats and 1 PWC on lake. Air tempurature - 80 degrees.
Mostly Sunny. Air temp. - 72 degrees. 6 Pleasure boats- 2 fishing boats- 2 PWC- 2 paddle boats- 1 loon on lake.
Sunny. Calm- no wind. 1 boat on lake. Air temp. 77 degrees. 2 young loons on lake. Lake is 1' low since May 2004.
Sunny. Air Temp. - 66 degrees. Calm. 2 boats fishing on lake. Temp. of silt on lake bottom - 56.1 degrees.
Sunny. ESE wind 0-5 MPH. 1 loon on lake.
Partly cloudy. 0-5 MPH SE wind. Two fishing boats on lake. Three loons on lake.
Clear. Wind SSW 0-5 mph. 1 loon- 1 muskrat- 1 boat on lake. Air temp. 78 degrees.
2 fishing boats on lake. 2 kayaks on lake. 2 loons on lake. 2 muskrats on lake. Lake is 8" lower than this spring. Air temp.  85 degrees.
5 MPH WSW wind. No boats on lake. Air temp. - 69 degrees. Sunny. Lake is 12" lower than this spring. 1 loon on lake.
1 pontoon boat on lake. 0-5 MPH variable direction wind. Mostly sunny. Air temp. 69 degrees. Water 12" lower than this spring.
0-5 MPH variable direction wind. Sunny. Air temp. 68 degrees. Water 14" lower than this spring. 1 fishing boat on lake.
WSW wind 5 MPH. Sunny. No boats on lake. Air temp. 49 degrees. Water 14" lower than this spring. Could not get sample during middle of month because of motor problems.
Sunny. 0-5 MPH variable direction wind. No boats on lake. Air temperature - 56 degrees.
Sunny. Calm. No boats on lake. Air temperature - 68 degrees.
Partly cloudy. 5-10 MPH SSE wind. Air temp. 78 degrees. 1 -pontoon boat- 2 - tubers- 1 - fishing boat on lake.
Partly cloudy. WSW wind 0-5 MPH. 2 PWC- 1 water skier- 2 fishing boats- 1 power boat on lake. Air temperature 74.8 degrees.

Sunny. 0-5 MPH variable direction wind. 2 loons on lake. Lake is 12" lower than at ice out. Temperature gauge went to 32.0 degrees when I lowered it to 19'. Took gauge and cable to Rhinelander and both were bad and were replaced.
Sunny. NW wind 5 MPH. 1 fishing boat- 1 boat pulling tubers- 1 boat pulling skier. Air temp 74.7 degrees. Lake went up 3" since last test.
Sunny. SW wind 0-5 MPH. Air temp. 72 degrees. 2 fishing boats on lake. 1 pair of loons on lake. Lake is down 13" since ice out.
sunny- calm- lake level down 15" since spring- top of weeds @ 14ft @ test site air temp. 71F- no boats on lake
Sunny. Calm. No boats on lake. 1 Loon on lake. Air temp. 42.5 degrees. Lake is 18" lower since ice out.
2 cormorants on lake. Partly high thin clouds. 0-5 MPH east wind. Air temp. 69 degrees. Lake is 18 inches below normal.
Variable clouds. 0-5 MPH North wind. Air temp. - 72.4 degrees. 2 fishing boats on lake. Lake is 15 inches below normal.
Clear sky. 5-10 MPH SW wind. 6 fishing boats and 2 pleasure boats on lake. Heavy algae bloom. Lake 15" below normal. Air temperature - 71 degrees.
Clear sky. 0-5 MPH WSW wind. 2 fishing boats on lake. Lake 17" low. Algae bloom started yesterday.
Partly cloudy. 0-5 MPH NNW wind. 1 fishing- 2 pleasure boats on lake. 2 loons on lake. Air temp. - 79 degrees. Lake is 21" low.
Sunny. 0-5 MPH NNE wind. Air temp. - 70.1 degrees. lake 24" low. No watercraft on lake. 1 loon on lake.
Sunny. Calm. 1 water skier- 4 fishing boats- 1 pleasure boat and 1 loon on lake. Lake is 24" below normal.
Partly high thin clouds. 0-5 MPH variable SE to NW winds. No boats on lake. Air temp. - 60 degrees. Lake is 14" low.
Variable clouds. 5-15 MPH SW wind. 1 fishing boat- 2 pleasure boats- 1 paddle boat on lake. Air temperature - 75 degrees. Lake is 12" low.
Clear. 0-5 MPH variable winds. 4 loons on lake. Moderate algae bloom. 2 fishing boats and 2 pleasure boats on lake. Lake is 15" low.

Clear. 0-5MPH variable wind. Moderate algae bloom. 1 fishing boat on lake. 1 loon on lake. Lake is 21" low. We have had as many as 6 loons swimming together in the late afternoon at times. Usually only have 4 loons swimming together in late afternoon most times.
Clear. 0-5 MPH SSE wind. 1 fishing boat on lake. Air temp. - 60 degrees. Lake is 24" low.
Sunny. 0-5 MPH variable wind. Air temp. - 64 degrees. Lake is 18 inches below normal.

Partly high thin clouds. 0-5 MPH variable winds.Air temp. - 84 degrees. 2 pleasure boats- 1 paddle boat- 2 fishing boats- 1 jet ski- 4 kayaks and two loons on lake. Lots of floating globular algae around lake. Lake is 18 inches below normal.
Partly cloudy. Variable 0-5 MPH wind. Air temp. - 72 degrees. 2 pleasure boats and 3 loons on lake. Moderate algae bloom. Lake is 21" below normal.
Calm winds. Clear skies. Lake is 24" below normal. Air temp. - 67.5 degrees. Moderate algae bloom. 2 PWC- 2 pleasure boats- 3 fishing boats and 2 loons on lake.
Clear sky. SW wind 5-10MPH. Air temperature - 66.5 degrees. 1 fishing boat and 1 loon on lake. Lake is 24" below normal.
Sunny. Gusting West Wind 5-15 MPH. Air temp. - 58 degrees. 1 pleasure boat on lake. Shoreline owners blowing leaves off of lawns into lake causing lots of debris in top three feet of water column.
Clear. Calm. Lake is 24" below normal. 6 fishing boats- 3 pleasure boats and 1 PWC on lake. Air Temperature - 76.5
Clear sky. 5 MPH N wind. Lake is 22" low. Air temp. - 69 degrees. 2 pleasure boats on lake.

Partly cloudy. 5 MPH SW wind. Air temp. - 77 degrees. 1 fishing boat- 1 pleasure boat and 2 kayaks on lake.Have not seen any loons on lake for the last three weeks. Lake is 12" low. Heavy algae bloom. Lake now has Eurasian Water Milfoil in two sections of the lake.
Mostly sunny. 0-5 MPH SW wind. Air Temp. - 77 degrees. Lake is 12" low. 1 fishing boat- 1 pleasure boat and 1 loon on lake. Heavy algae bloom.
Few Hi-Cirrus clouds. 5-10 MPH SE wind. 1 fishing boat on lake. Water level is 12" below normal.

Clear. SSW wind 5-10 MPH. Air Temp. 74 degrees. 1 fishing boat - 1 pontoon boat - 1 PWC on lake. Lake is 8" below normal. Clear. SSW wind 5-10 MPH. Air Temp. 74 degrees. 1 fishing boat - 1 pontoon boat - 1 PWC on lake. Lake is 8" below normal. Large algae bloom.

Mostly clear. 5-10 MPH North wind. Lake is 12" below normal.  1 fishing boat- 1 PWC- 1 pontoon boat- 1 pleasure boat pulling tubers and 1 pleasure boat pulling water skiers on lake. Air temp. - 73.7 degrees.
Mostly clear. 5-10 MPH west wind. Lake is 14" below normal. Air temperature - 71 degrees. 1 pleasure boat on lake with water skiers. Heavy algae bloom.
Clouds 50/50. SE wind - 7-12 MPH. Air temp. - 50 degrees. Lake is 14" low. 1 pontoon boat- 1 fishing boat- 2 work boats (hand-pulling EWM) and 1 loon on lake.
Clouds 50/50. NNW wind at 0-5 MPH.Air temperature - 42 degrees. Lake is 17" low. No boats or loons on lake today.
Clear sky. 5-10 MPH N wind. 1 DNR fisheries boat on lake. 2 Hooded Mergansers and 6 Common Mergansers on lake. Lake is 1' below normal.
Partly cloudy. Wind - SW 0-5 mph. Air temp. - 70 degrees. 2 pontoons- 2 pleasure boats and 1 fishing boat on lake. Lake is 18" below normal.
Sunny. 0-5MPH variable wind. 2-PWC- 2-pleasure boats-1-canoe- 1 loon on lake. Lake is 12" below normal.

Clear skies.   SW wind - 5-15MPH   Lake is 18" below normal.   Air temp. - 81.5 degrees.   2 pleasure boats and 1 water skiing boat on lake.   There has been one loon with two chicks on the lake the last 45 days.
CLEAR + SUNNY. 0-5 MPH VARIABLE WIND. 2 LOONS ON LAKE. NO BOATS ON LAKE..
Mostly sunny. 0-5 MPH variable wind. Air temp. 74 degrees. 1 pleasure boat tubing- 1 fishing boat on lake. Lake is 9 inches below normal.
Mostly sunny. 0-5 MPH variable wind. Air temp. - 73 degrees. Lake is 8 inches low. 2 pleasure boats pulling tubes. 2 fishing boats. 1 pontoon boat. 2 kayaks. Moderate algae bloom.
Mostly sunny. 0-5 MPH variable wind. Air temp. - 73 degrees. 2 pleasure boates- 1 pontoon boat- 1 paddle surfer- 2 people on a swimming raft crossing lake. Lake is 8 inches low.

Mostly sunny. Variable S - SW 5 MPH gusting to 10 MPH wind. 2 loons- 2 pleasure boats- 1 pontoon boat on lake. Air tempurature - 75 degrees.  Before I did these tests- there were three boats out helping with hand-pulling EWM.
Mostly sunny. Variable winds 0-5 MPH. 6 pontoons- 2 fishing boats- 4 recreational boats- 3 PWC- i paddle board on lake. Light algae bloom. Air tempurature - 79 degrees.

Air temp. - 76 degrees. 05-MPH ESE wind. 2 pleasure boats- 1 fishing boat- 1 pontoon boat- 1 PWC and 2 loons on lake. Partly to mostly cloudy. Waited until sun came out from under a cloud when I made the seechi depth test.

Air Temp. - 72 degrees. 5-10 MPH North wind. Lake is 8 inches below normal level. Partly/Mostly cloudy. 2 fishing boats- 1 water ski boat- 1 pontoon boat- 1 boat from Onterra doing Point Intersect study on lake.

Air temp. - 73.4 degrees. SW wind 5-10 MPH.Partly cloudy high thin clouds. No boats on lake. No loons on lake. High small algae bloom. I have never seen the lake so murky in many years as it is this year. Lake is 8.5" below normal.
Lake is 6" below normal. 7 fishing boats on lake fishing for Musky. 2 loons on lake. Clear and sunny. 0-5 MPH West wind.

column1: This year has been the worst year that I can remember for waterm clarity. The lake seems to have had a continuous algae bloom all summer long. When standing on my pier- the water is about five feet deep and you could never see the bottom through clear water. There was never any large floating algae- just small micro particles all the way down in the water coulumn.

column2: No boats on lake. Lots of ducks flying around lake this Spring.
No loons on lake. One pontoon boat cruising around shoreline.
Moderate algae bloom. Variable direction wind 0-5 MPH. 1 pontoon- 1 pleasure boat and 1 loon on lake. Could not find Pale-yellow Iris on North shore of lake.
Mostly clear sky. Air temperature - 73.7 Degrees. 0-5 MPH SW wind. One loon with a juvenile swimming near boat landing. 1 Pontoon and 1 pleasure boat pulling tubers on lake.
SE wind - 5-10 MPH. Clear skies. Air temp. - 74.6 degrees. 1 loon and 6 fishing boats on lake. Weeds are very sparse this year at the Deep Hole.

Variable 0-5 MPH wind. Clear sky. Air temp. - 54.2. Two pontoon boats on lake. Two loons on lake. This his the first time since I started doing Self-Help Testing- that I did not pull up one weeds of any kind on my anchor when I pulled it up after finishing my tests. The weeds have been very sparse and not as high this year. Again we had the milky looking and constant algea in the lake. Water temperatures did not get up into the normal or high temperature range during the summer.

column1: Lake has truned over. Only .5 degrees between top and bottom temperature.

column2: Partly high thin clouds. Variable direction 0-5 MPH winds. Air Temperature - 57 degrees. No boats on lake. There have been two loons on the lake this past week.
Partly high thin clouds. Variable direction 5-10 MPH winds. Air temperature - 83.4 degrees. 3 fishing boats- 1 pontoon boat fishing and 1 pontoon just cruising around the lake. No loons observed.
Sunny. 0-5MPH wind. Air temperature - 74 degrees. Moderate algae bloom. 1 pontoon fishing and 1 PWC on lake.

Clear sky. 5-10MPH variable direction wind. Air temperature - 85.2 degrees. 1 pontoon- 1 PWC- 1 fishing boat on lake. Had to tow in one boat that signaled for help. Was out from boat landing about 500 feet. Engine quit running and asked if his plug was in the transom. He said yes. The bilge pump was running all the way i and asked him again if the plug was in. He looked this time and said that it was not. They had a hard time getting the boat on the trailer and finally left. When I left- it showed that the bilge pump was pumping out water for about 1/4 mile and the bilge was draining out for about 1/2 mile/
Air Temperature - 78.2 degrees. Mostly clear skies. Variable direction winds - 0-5 MPH. 3 fishing boats- 1 pontoon boat- 1 pleasure boat- 1 PWC on lake. Light algae bloom.
